Qualification Resources:

  • Discovery/Pre-call Prep Guide
  • ASE/BDR Discovery Certification

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Qualification Coaching Questions:

  • Describe the biggest business problems the customer is trying to solve.
  • Does the customer recognize that they have a business problem to solve?
  • Who is responsible for solving the business problem/pain? 
  • How will doing nothing impact the customers business?

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Discovery Coaching Questions:

  • What are the quantified impacts of these business problems?
  • Describe the competitive landscape.
  • How are we uniquely & comparatively differentiated from the competition?
  • What is the customers compelling event?
  • What formal Decision Criteria have we identified?

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
POC Scoping Resources:

  • Mutual Action Plan
  • Evaluation Plan Scoping Guide
  • Evaluation Plan Template

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
POC Scoping Coaching Questions:

  • How have we tested our Champion?
  • What evidence do we have that he/she is a Champion?
  • How have we influenced the Decision Criteria?
  • Who is funding this initiative?
  • Describe the steps & the players in the Economic Buyers Decision Process.
  • What information is our Champion using to sell internally?
  • What success Metrics are most relevant?

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Proof of Concept Resources:

  • POC / Evaluation Summary Presentation

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Proof of Concept Coaching Questions:

  • Describe the outcome of our proposed solution discussion. What are the next steps?
  • Have we validated the customers Required Capabilities?
  • Is the Retool SE prepared to deliver the POC according to the customers Required Capabilities?
  • Walk me through the procurement process. What are the paper/contract requirements?
  • How have we validated these processes with our Champion?
  • Who signs the contract? Explain how you will access them.

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Validating Business Case / Negotiating Resources:

  • Executive partnership / business case summary deck
  • SKU Catalogue
  • Building Order Forms

componentInstanceProperties.name: richTextValue
componentInstanceProperties.value:
Validating Business Case / Negotiating Coaching Questions:

  • Did we obtain verbal agreement from the Economic Buyer at our specified price point? 
  • Why would the customer not move forward with us?
  • Have we provided the necessary information to our SE?
  • Have we walked through the Mutual Action Plan and verified a close date?
  • What is the customers best alternative to a negotiated agreement?
  • Who within our network has negotiated with this company before?
  • Has the customer committed all resources to move forward (legal, marketing, IT, etc.)?
  • What challenges are we likely to encounter when it is time to get the final signature?
  • Is there anything that would prevent the customer from signing?
